{"id": "ChIJ-eppGgB_hYARze809sxtDMA", "rating": 4.4, "userRatingCount": 97, "displayName": {"text": "Yume Mori Matcha", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJ-eppGgB_hYARze809sxtDMA/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pJeFVrVjBNR0p4U205T1RuTmZjbFJpVFZoUVdtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Highly recommend the Kumo matcha. There is almost no bitterness with just the right amount of sweetness.\n\nTwo self ordering tablets inside, no cashier. Expect a crammed pickup station since that’s right in front of the line at the entrance. Have your phone ready to show them your order number when picking up because they will ALWAYS ASK.\n\nWaited around 10 min to order drinks but another 20 for the drink to be made. This was on a Sunday around 1:30pm. After we left the line was 4x as long.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Highly recommend the Kumo matcha. There is almost no bitterness with just the right amount of sweetness.\n\nTwo self ordering tablets inside, no cashier. Expect a crammed pickup station since that’s right in front of the line at the entrance. Have your phone ready to show them your order number when picking up because they will ALWAYS ASK.\n\nWaited around 10 min to order drinks but another 20 for the drink to be made. This was on a Sunday around 1:30pm. After we left the line was 4x as long.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "KD", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106345724218462725253/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU1sVK1I8iWi2-NklURj2UVbEqx1tkwLpA-Vy2NVk3uN5b7lzo=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-04T06:49:13.807206170Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pJeFVrVjBNR0p4U205T1RuTmZjbFJpVFZoUVdtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pJeFVrVjBNR0p4U205T1RuTmZjbFJpVFZoUVdtYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857f001a69eaf9:0xc00c6dccf634efcd"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ-eppGgB_hYARze809sxtDMA/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xWaWVIWklOVXgxWXpCMlZXcERSRXMxWW1ZeVMxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I saw people queuing up outside and I thought \"theres no way its worth that wait\". Then I waited, got my drink and crepe, and confirmed that it was absolutely worth the wait. Matcha is super high quality and delicious and the crepes were shockingly good. Way spongier than a normal cake and the matcha creme brulee one I had was incredible.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I saw people queuing up outside and I thought \"theres no way its worth that wait\". Then I waited, got my drink and crepe, and confirmed that it was absolutely worth the wait. Matcha is super high quality and delicious and the crepes were shockingly good. Way spongier than a normal cake and the matcha creme brulee one I had was incredible.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Alex Locke", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104694067540380198340/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXiT9qeylytuCD0Yf3iUg_K-2pGVjpqmGwN0P22fGC-rXbIYSIk8Q=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-27T06:43:07.280397821Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xWaWVIWklOVXgxWXpCMlZXcERSRXMxWW1ZeVMxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xWaWVIWklOVXgxWXpCMlZXcERSRXMxWW1ZeVMxRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857f001a69eaf9:0xc00c6dccf634efcd"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ-eppGgB_hYARze809sxtDMA/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s1bmRUSXRjRlo0VUVkcllTMDFUMnA0ZG5WclpYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "I tried this place 3 times. I like the double matcha (mie) since it is strong, creamy, & flavourful.  The strawberry matcha was off my list since it tasted ok.\nThey always ran out of crepes around 2-3pm. So I couldn’t get it for the first 2 times.\nWe got our crepes the last time since we came early but be prepared: your pocket could burn out here. *The cost of a crepe is around $10.95 plus tax. We paid almost $26 for 2 crepes plus tips.\nThe crepes were pre make so it was cold.  I couldn’t finish one crepe since it was too creamy & I got indigestion later. Recommend buy 1 crepe to share for 2 people.\n*The drinks here also are expensive & very small.\nOverall, it’s a place to taste matcha sometimes, not often since it’s expensive here.\n*** The downside is that they only have 1 kiosk to order & it took 1 customer (especially new one) around 7min to order while all baristas were watching, staring, rolling eyes & laughing at them. I didn’t like that kind of services.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I tried this place 3 times. I like the double matcha (mie) since it is strong, creamy, & flavourful.  The strawberry matcha was off my list since it tasted ok.\nThey always ran out of crepes around 2-3pm. So I couldn’t get it for the first 2 times.\nWe got our crepes the last time since we came early but be prepared: your pocket could burn out here. *The cost of a crepe is around $10.95 plus tax. We paid almost $26 for 2 crepes plus tips.\nThe crepes were pre make so it was cold.  I couldn’t finish one crepe since it was too creamy & I got indigestion later. Recommend buy 1 crepe to share for 2 people.\n*The drinks here also are expensive & very small.\nOverall, it’s a place to taste matcha sometimes, not often since it’s expensive here.\n*** The downside is that they only have 1 kiosk to order & it took 1 customer (especially new one) around 7min to order while all baristas were watching, staring, rolling eyes & laughing at them. I didn’t like that kind of services.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "M M", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106909089165033554639/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJWi_nPuwYF2WE7Q9bGtS_ZxeCRydrLyFtyJF7Fzr_tIX3ezw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-07T07:26:45.941774250Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s1bmRUSXRjRlo0VUVkcllTMDFUMnA0ZG5WclpYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s1bmRUSXRjRlo0VUVkcllTMDFUMnA0ZG5WclpYYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857f001a69eaf9:0xc00c6dccf634efcd"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ-eppGgB_hYARze809sxtDMA/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GRmNXTkNiekprUVZsNGMzWkljbE5sYTFKcU4zYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "There was always a line when I passed by, so I decided to give it a try!\nI ordered the Cold Whisk Matcha with shizu matchia, oat milk and regular sweet. The drink had a rich umami flavor with an earthy taste and a light bitterness. It tasted great but the regular sweet was too sweet for me. Next time, I might choose no sugar or they offer more sweetness options. I would also like to try their Koku matcha drink next time!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "There was always a line when I passed by, so I decided to give it a try!\nI ordered the Cold Whisk Matcha with shizu matchia, oat milk and regular sweet. The drink had a rich umami flavor with an earthy taste and a light bitterness. It tasted great but the regular sweet was too sweet for me. Next time, I might choose no sugar or they offer more sweetness options. I would also like to try their Koku matcha drink next time!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Alice Hou", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/118209491174900771446/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVDlKWFVtHXfi5RlpYkOa9AJ3kzi4zvRKi2-61rc7TPsbKteJB7RQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-18T19:15:42.882856614Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GRmNXTkNiekprUVZsNGMzWkljbE5sYTFKcU4zYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GRmNXTkNiekprUVZsNGMzWkljbE5sYTFKcU4zYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857f001a69eaf9:0xc00c6dccf634efcd"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ-eppGgB_hYARze809sxtDMA/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pRNFZqWkxWM2hKU2tSamVsRnpMV2hHUm1WNVZHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "9 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I have to say that Pete, the owner of this Matcha Cafe really knows his matcha! Yume Mori brings the traditional taste of Japanese ceremonial grade Matcha to Berkeley! Yume Mori’s cafe from their understated decor to their beautifully crafted and tasty drinks and crepes is reminiscent of a Matcha shop you would see walking on the shotengai in Kamakura. This cafe is worth standing in line for! Thanks for bringing me such a nostalgic experience!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I have to say that Pete, the owner of this Matcha Cafe really knows his matcha! Yume Mori brings the traditional taste of Japanese ceremonial grade Matcha to Berkeley! Yume Mori’s cafe from their understated decor to their beautifully crafted and tasty drinks and crepes is reminiscent of a Matcha shop you would see walking on the shotengai in Kamakura. This cafe is worth standing in line for! Thanks for bringing me such a nostalgic experience!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Brenda Bohn", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109794467394608439594/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW1VbcAPgQYBlUtxe77atopgVanQ1I5cc5J8YgETRjTqJEznh2b=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2025-09-27T23:59:25.141625595Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/re